title: Paquito d'Rivera on the clarinet

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/69.0.3497.33 Safari/537.36

description:
In this interview done during the Jazz Cruise in 2016, saxophonist and clarinetist Paquito D’Rivera talks about the challenges and rewards of the clarinet. D’Rivera was performing on the cruise with his sextet.

Interview by Irene Lee.  Video production by Lee Mergner & Melissa Mergner. Thanks to Michael Lazaroff and the production team of Entertainment Cruise Productions. 

For more information about Paquito D’Rivera, go to www.paquitodrivera.com

For more information about the Jazz Cruise, go to www.thejazzcruise.com

For more information about JazzTimes, go to www.jazztimes.com
